text: Dmitriyevka () is a rural locality (a village) in Nordovsky Selsoviet, Meleuzovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 356 as of 2010. == Geography == It is located 32 km from Meleuz, 10 km from Nordovka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Meleuzovsky District
title: Dmitriyevka, Nordovsky Selsoviet, Meleuzovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
